  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个安全架构的流程图，核心是从OAuth2认证开始，然后分支到零信任策略评估。你能帮我搭建这个框架吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，OAuth2作为入口节点。我想确认一下：OAuth2之后是一个判断节点还是直接连到零信任？通常认证会有成功失败的分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，OAuth2后面应该是一个菱形判断节点，成功走零信任，失败的话直接走防火墙阻断。这样比较合理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把OAuth2做成矩形入口，后面接菱形判断，两条分支分别标注Success和Failure，失败分支连到防火墙。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来对，但零信任节点之后呢？我觉得应该再回到OAuth2做一次令牌校验，形成闭环验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_OAuth2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加，零信任节点后连回OAuth2。接下来从二次校验的OAuth2再延伸到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_OAuth2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后进入加密层，Security_Encryption。但这里有个复杂的部分——加密之后要进入一个策略评估的子图，里面包含匹配判断和入侵检测的多层逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Policy Evaluation",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "策略评估子图我理解，但想确认结构：加密节点E进入子图后，第一个节点是另一个零信任判断F吗？然后F分支到G和H？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，F是策略匹配判断，Match走G回到OAuth2，No Match走H再到防火墙判断。H又有两条分支都连到入侵检测I和J。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "子图结构已搭建，标注为Policy Evaluation。G、I、J三条线最后都汇聚到同一个加密节点K，然后K再到最终的入侵检测L。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Policy Evaluation",
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程结构对了。但我们得区分一下视觉层次，入口、判断、策略评估和最终节点用不同颜色。",
